          <div class="testimonial-stars">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled">star</span>
          </div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">"Je perdais 15 clients par mois sans le savoir. Après la méthode, mes appels ont augmenté de 60% en 3 semaines."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Fleuriste</strong>
            <span>Chartres (28)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-result">
            <span class="badge badge--success">+60% d'appels entrants</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled">star</span>
